---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - U-STAT">
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden w-full min-h-screen">
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-[500px] bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,var(--color-blue-600)_0%,transparent_70%)] opacity-10 dark:opacity-20 pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>

    <header
      class="container mx-auto px-6 py-6 flex justify-between items-center relative z-10"
    >
      <a
        href="/"
        class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter select-none hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity"
      >
        <span class="text-[var(--accent-color)]">U</span>-STAT
      </a>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="text-sm font-bold opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
        >Back to Home</a
      >
    </header>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20 relative z-10 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tight">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert lg:prose-xl space-y-8 opacity-90">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Data Storage</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            By default, everything is stored locally on your device. If you
            uninstall the app or clear your cache, your teams, games, etc is all
            gone forever.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Link Sharing</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            If you choose to share a game or team via a link, that data is
            stored on a database for 30 days.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-4 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
            <li>
              <strong>Public Access:</strong> Anyone with the shared link can view
              the team and game data associated with it. This includes player names,
              game stats, lines, etc.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Expiration:</strong> Shared links are deleted after 30 days.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Permissions</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            This app does not require any special permissions to function. It
            doesn't have access to your system files, location, camera, or
            microphone.
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4 italic opacity-80">
            Note: If you use the "Export to CSV" feature, the app generates a
            file for you to download. This is a one-way action; the app cannot
            see or access any other files on your device.
          </p>
        </section>

        <footer class="pt-20 text-sm opacity-50">
          Last updated: Feb 10, 2026.
        </footer>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
